verbose_text: Dietary intake that includes consumption of any combination of amino acids and carbohydrates during a stage of resistance exercise maximizes insulin 's influence on tissue anabolism and protein synthesis by decreasing protein catabolism [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR] and utilizing enhanced blood flow in the skeletal muscles [XREF_BIBR].
